data.description: Welcome to your newly renovated bungalow located only a few blocks from Lake Weeks. The 2/1 charming home is move-in ready.  Roof, AC, siding, floors, decking, and driveway are all new and ready for the next owner. The well thought out floor plan makes the space feel airy and light. The kitchen is stylish and offers all the modern amenities for those that love to cook.  Located off the kitchen is a dining room that flows directly into the living area.  The bedrooms have lots of natural light with ample closet space.  The newly reimagined bathroom feels spacious and updated with contemporary finishes. The exterior offers a new porch and a driveway with beautiful pavers. Off the drive, the walkway carries and extends around the entire home.  The home has nice curb appeal with lots of mature tress and fresh sod. Easy access to major roads and shopping. Come be a part of the Lake Weeks lake community! Ask about creative financing options.
